{
  "stem": "22174.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was frequently attacked by-- by airplanes by German [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so there-- there was one gun on the port, a big double-barreled Fiat gun.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was manned by-- by a group of Scotsmen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was attacked by planes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They came out from the sun and attacked them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But it was so clumsy, that gun, so when the-- the planes turned around, and then came and attacked them from the back, because they-- they couldn't work that big gun so quick, you know.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was too slow to turn around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So if they wanted [INAUDIBLE] protect from the rear, so the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We stayed [INAUDIBLE] close to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So they asked us for volunteers to protect their back, to protect their rear.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I volunteered for that [INAUDIBLE] gun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We had a-- we had a Lewis gun, a machine gun, a British machine gun.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we took that, and we-- we took a position next to that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And-- and-- and watched their rear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And one time we shot down-- shot down a-- a German plane.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I didn't shoot it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But there was a sergeant from our-- our company, my company, and he shot it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But I-- I served the magazines.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I filled the magazines.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And, at that time, we were [? technically ?] about 60-- 60-- 60 planes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we had about 13-- 13 bombs right next to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when the-- the rest of my company, the fellows, they saw that, from the [? body ?] where they stayed, and they thought we were already gone, we were dead, you know, killed because it was all surrounded by-- by-- by the explosions, by the dust, you know?",
      "word_count": 49
    }
  ],
